Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:17.65,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:20.69,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just a track meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.00,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Right, just a track meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:06.81,Episode-Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(733,476)}Episode 5:\N"Hinode Bridge"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.50,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,He's smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:48.27,Main,Guy with gun,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.40,Main,Guy with gun,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:23.71,Main,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:25.52,Main,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,Long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:26.14,Main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:29.17,Main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:32.20,Main,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:34.43,Main,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,Must be hard to get back into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:35.61,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.03,Main,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,Is that—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:39.96,Main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:42.84,Main,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Matsuda. I'm run sprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:44.46,Main,Guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nagai. I do hurdles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:45.57,Main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hyouno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.81,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yukinari's—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.55,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares, Yanagi. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.96,Main,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,They call each other by their first names.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:56.53,Main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinari, don't use up all your energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:03:59.64,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.91,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,get some release, too, \Nor it'll hurt your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.95,Main,Guy 4,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks were awesome the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.78,Main,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.07,Main,Guy 4,0000,0000,0000,,Next year, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:23.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really huge up close!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:25.20,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you should have said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:26.99,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to start rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.59,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.71,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered I have \Nsomething to do. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:23.45,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.56,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,is Hiro-kun on another...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:30.03,Main,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,A date, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:34.30,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind me asking, whom's he with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:36.32,Main,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:38.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.85,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:44.23,Main,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.23,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.45,Main,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,You've become even
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.46,Main,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,more of a lady lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.69,Main,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,Summer is the season of love, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.09,Main,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I've said too \Nmuch to a dear customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:58.08,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:02.08,Main,Grandpa,0000,0000,0000,,Let me bring you a cookie \Nto make up for it, on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:03.42,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:05.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.64,Sacchan,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.72,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.20,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:22.03,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Who? Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.61,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:33.83,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You chased me down all \Nout of breath just to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:39.04,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.60,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you've done it before, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:44.63,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to the plaster figure in the art room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.86,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,to gather your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:47.86,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.18,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Touko says she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:53.05,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,So are you saying I don't have to respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:09.28,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Is Sacchan in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:10.87,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-chan's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:12.66,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She was coming today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.02,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:18.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.86,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.68,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.68,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:38.49,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:45.56,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.18,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:48.92,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:55.70,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.71,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:07:59.33,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.70,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:01.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:28.75,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki hurt his leg during \Nthe summer of first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.07,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,He's rehabilitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:34.81,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,There was a joint middle-school\Nand high-school track meet today,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:36.82,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,but it didn't go too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.23,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-kun has
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.63,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,a date today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:48.47,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:52.55,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But I was already supposed \Nto come over today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:57.07,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan, are you going out with Hiro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.82,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,He was here until earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.29,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So many surprises today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.62,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd be going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.31,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.56,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-chan, you've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:12.40,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I'm going out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.75,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,We were just reading together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.89,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.54,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it wouldn't be anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:24.15,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,And you? Have you met with \Nthat guy since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:27.33,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:30.78,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okikura-kun seems stern,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:32.63,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought maybe he has a nice side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.09,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:35.88,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,And he's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:39.36,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. No, no, no. It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:42.24,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:52.28,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be in the \Nhospital for a while soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:56.99,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for tests, so it's \Nnothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.28,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:02.73,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's somewhere I want to go \Nwith you when I'm discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:03.86,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:05.75,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:11.04,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could see the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:14.15,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I think Yuki's really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:17.01,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants to know the future, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.00,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously not going to say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:23.90,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nah,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.56,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I won't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.43,Italics,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Okikura residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:13.65,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okikura-kun? It's Fukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.73,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Can we meet up for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:21.17,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I know. What you said \Nto me the other night...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.74,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.93,Italics,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru is out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:30.46,Italics,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse my late introduction. \NI'm Kakeru's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.46,Italics,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let him know you \Ncalled when he gets home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:44.08,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:11:59.39,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:06.53,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.49,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You would do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:08.49,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.60,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.07,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought maybe I'd read for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.65,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,So you bought it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.13,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,No, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.12,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,There's no chance you'd read Camus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.69,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Camus. Camus! {\i1}The Myth of Sisyphus{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:22.84,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,It makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.91,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's that tragic glasses girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.54,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Fukami here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:38.11,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Sorry, I was out earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.57,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:44.87,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,My dad said he's sorry for \Ntroubling a young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.40,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:49.16,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It was my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.00,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to come over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:53.63,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:56.33,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,my dad says he wants to cook \Nfor you to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.67,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:00.54,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's been living alone for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.80,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,He's good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.22,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.47,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:08.04,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:11.22,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I need to tell you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.88,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how to get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.66,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:19.48,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.55,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Touko Fukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.71,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.97,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.59,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as a light snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:28.74,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:33.25,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, make Fukami-san \Nat home in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:37.14,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She's half my guest today, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.93,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll keep her company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:44.01,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.82,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:00.69,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:02.02,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:05.31,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,When it rained the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.28,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,on the road to Kirinkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.43,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.40,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't hugging her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:17.61,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I just caught her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.90,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,"Hugging"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.57,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,She'd hurt her leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:21.62,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You know about that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:24.10,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm done talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.58,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,She nearly fell over on the steep road.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.10,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:39.44,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,But the reason I wanted you over today \Nis to talk about her—Takayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:43.57,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Takayama is going to \Nconfess to Yukinari Imi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:45.15,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:49.24,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I said, Takayama is going \Nto confess to Yukinari Imi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.81,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:52.90,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:54.17,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:55.16,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,She told me herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:58.65,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,She told me to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.97,Flashback,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to tell Touko about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:08.89,Flashback,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Because—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:10.18,Flashback,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.89,Flashback,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk, statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.05,Flashback,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:41.33,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:44.33,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kakeru,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:47.42,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,this is a good opportunity. \NWhy don't you get a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.93,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.88,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really that useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:54.43,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Well, I might die without one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:58.81,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Would anyone ever call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:04.40,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yana-chan's leg all better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.39,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.80,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:10.45,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I know your boyfriend's there,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:13.10,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,but you've seriously got \Nears all over the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.49,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,How often are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.71,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Three days a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:19.71,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,They were such a cute couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.82,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,They're both remarried and have kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:26.51,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,There they are amidst \Ntheir complicated family,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.95,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,like leaves in a cold blast, like a boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:31.30,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,their hearts tossed in a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.91,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:37.16,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:42.15,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I had such a treat today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:43.69,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.16,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.32,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I found an interesting place the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.08,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It's nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:54.58,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,When I found it, I knew \NI had to take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.22,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I've been meaning to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.00,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.58,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.07,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here. I'll get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:11.23,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything today.  \NThe meal was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:14.60,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Say hi to your dad for me. \NI'll be heading home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:15.73,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:20.88,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,She still hasn't told me what \Nshe wanted to talk to me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:42.37,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagi. You haven't made it home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.20,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm resting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:50.63,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I take a break, \Neat, drink some water,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:52.28,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,and get ready for the rest of the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:55.59,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:58.52,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,There was something I wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:08.21,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.21,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:14.13,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I know you like Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:16.55,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I know you confessed to her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:19.66,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's going to be painful for me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:22.77,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,to live with you after you reject me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:25.88,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,We're family, as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.72,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I know what your answer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:32.97,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I would have been really \Nhappy if you gave up Touko for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.41,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,but I would have lost respect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.72,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.32,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going \Nto happen to us now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:43.72,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,but this is where I move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:49.87,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.31,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll head home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:57.02,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,If I see you there, I hope we can \Nkeep things the way they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:13.58,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I overheard something some high school girls
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.15,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,said at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:19.22,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,One of them said, "1221, year of the Joukyu war."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.76,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,High school girls are busy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:24.70,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, can you set up the \Nchopsticks and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.43,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:45.77,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, come help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.49,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:51.69,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.25,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.25,0:23:32.32,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't explain anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:34.47,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a total idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:35.74,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:37.93,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the school yard. \NLet's put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:38.39,Episode-Title - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 6\N"Punch"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:40.39,Episode-Title - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,
